text: Mugdha Vilas Joshi (born 10 November 1993) is a Maharashtrian cricketer. She Plays for Mumbai and West Zone. She has played 11First-class, 41 List A and 34Women's Twenty20 matches. == References == Category:1993 births Category:West Zone women cricketers Category:Mumbai women cricketers Category:Living people
